1
00:00:07,082 --> 00:00:08,890
Hi, Michael. Hi, Danny.
你好,Michael.你好,Danny.

2
00:00:09,186 --> 00:00:09,700
Hi, Nancy.
你好,Nancy.

3
00:00:09,946 --> 00:00:11,450
Yvonne, have you met our new tenants?
Yvonne,见过我们的新房客了吗?

4
00:00:11,662 --> 00:00:12,124
Not yet.
还没有.

5
00:00:12,435 --> 00:00:14,721
Yvonne Washington, Michael Chung and Danny DeMarco. 
Yvonne Washington, Michael Chung和Danny DeMarco. 

6
00:00:14,968 --> 00:00:15,960
They moved in last weekend. 
他们是上周末搬进来的.

7
00:00:16,187 --> 00:00:18,700
It was last weekend, right?
是上周末,对吗?

8
00:00:18,960 --> 00:00:20,250
Just last Saturday.
就在上周六.

9
00:00:20,557 --> 00:00:23,623
Of course. How could I forget that sofa?
当然.我怎么可能忘记那张沙发呢?

10
00:00:23,994 --> 00:00:25,990
How did you finally get it into the apartment?
最后你们是怎么把它弄进房间的?

11
00:00:26,349 --> 00:00:28,361
Very slowly and very carefully.
慢慢地,非常小心地搬进去的.

12
00:00:28,769 --> 00:00:30,142
Yvonne, do you live here, too?
Yvonne,你也住这儿吗?

13
00:00:30,376 --> 00:00:32,628
No, no. Nancy and I are business partners, 
不,不.Nancy和我是生意伙伴,

14
00:00:32,891 --> 00:00:34,007
so I'm here quite a bit.
所以我经常来这.

15
00:00:34,385 --> 00:00:35,352
Oh. What kind of business?
Oh. 你们做哪一行?

16
00:00:35,647 --> 00:00:36,913
Interior design. 
室内装潢设计.

17
00:00:37,298 --> 00:00:38,804
Do you need help with your new place?
你们的新地方需要装修吗?

18
00:00:39,143 --> 00:00:41,903
With our furniture? Impossible!
就我们这些家具?不可能!

19
00:00:42,228 --> 00:00:44,418
Oh, I hardly think so.
Oh,我不这么认为.

20
00:00:44,718 --> 00:00:45,879
You haven't seen the sofa.
你没见过我们的沙发.

21
00:00:46,178 --> 00:00:50,375
Besides, I'm sure Lisa will help us redecorate.
而且,我相信Lisa会帮我们重新装饰的.

22
00:00:50,663 --> 00:00:52,500
-Lisa?   -Lisa's my girlfriend.
-Lisa?   -Lisa是我的女朋友. 

23
00:00:52,807 --> 00:00:54,883
Just getting home from work, Danny?
刚下班回家吗,Danny?

24
00:00:55,257 --> 00:00:56,759
Yeah. I'm beat.
是的.我累死了.

25
00:00:57,052 --> 00:00:58,086
Where do you work?
你在哪里工作?

26
00:00:58,310 --> 00:01:00,027
Kinko's. The night shift.
在Kinko复印社.夜班.

27
00:01:00,244 --> 00:01:01,597
You too, Michael?
你也是吗,Michael?

28
00:01:01,880 --> 00:01:04,778
Oh no. Michael is a serious film maker.
Oh不是.Michael可是位严肃的电影制片人.

29
00:01:05,064 --> 00:01:06,973
-Danny...   -Really?
-Danny...   -真的吗?

30
00:01:07,278 --> 00:01:09,170
I'm a graduate student in Film Studies.
我是研究生,电影研究专业.

31
00:01:09,385 --> 00:01:10,686
And I do work at night, occasionally.
有时晚上我也打些工.

32
00:01:11,003 --> 00:01:13,184
Actually, Yvonne, we've got to run. 
真的,Yvonne,我们得走了.

33
00:01:13,468 --> 00:01:15,266
Everything OK in the apartment?
公寓的情况都好吗?

34
00:01:15,526 --> 00:01:16,330
So far, so good.
到目前为止还行.

35
00:01:16,400 --> 00:01:17,700
Good. We'll see you later.
好.那再见了.

36
00:01:17,868 --> 00:01:18,700
-Nice to meet you.  -Bye.
-很高兴认识你们.    -再见.

37
00:01:20,056 --> 00:01:21,533
It must be hard to work all night.
整夜工作一定很累.

38
00:01:21,792 --> 00:01:23,600
Unless you sleep all day.
除非你白天睡一整天.

